     - Update compat from 5 to 7.
     - B-D to debhelper (>= 7.0.50) to be able to use overrides.
     - Use debian/docs and debian/manpages to control dh_* accordingly.
     - Rework debian/rules.
     - Drop cdbs from B-D.

